        <Parent_String>critical theories (dialectical critiques) [300065248], historical, theoretical, and critical concepts [300056177], concepts in the arts and humanities [300056107], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
